<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>まとめ練習 - ランディングページ</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@latest/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="container my-4">
    <div class="p-5 text-center bg-light rounded-3">
      <h1 class="display-6 fw-bold">新作コレクション</h1>
      <p class="lead">季節のおすすめをチェック</p>
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">今すぐ購入</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="container my-4">
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="display-6">🔥</div>
          <h3 class="h5 mt-2">人気商品</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">売れ筋アイテムをまとめて紹介</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="display-6">⚡</div>
          <h3 class="h5 mt-2">高速配送</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">最短翌日でお届け</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="display-6">💳</div>
          <h3 class="h5 mt-2">安心決済</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">主要な支払い方法に対応</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
